INSERT INTO pages (id, section, title_zh, title_en, content_zh, content_en, sort_order) VALUES ('party', 'party', '黨的建設', 'Party Building', '中國航天國際控股有限公司（航天控股）始終堅持黨的領導，以高質量黨建引領企業高質量發展。公司黨委深入學習貫徹習近平新時代中國特色社會主義思想，全面落實新時代黨的建設總要求，把黨的政治建設擺在首位，推動黨建工作與生產經營深度融合。

本欄目展示公司黨建動態、黨員先鋒模範事蹟、職工之家建設成果及團青工作風采，全面反映航天控股黨建工作成效。', 'China Aerospace International Holdings Limited (CASIL) always adheres to the leadership of the Party and drives high-quality corporate development through high-quality Party building. The Company''s Party Committee thoroughly studies and implements Xi Jinping Thought on Socialism with Chinese Characteristics for a New Era, fully implements the general requirements for Party building in the new era, prioritizes the political construction of the Party, and promotes the deep integration of Party building work with production and operations.

This section showcases the Company''s Party building news, exemplary deeds of Party member pioneers, achievements in staff home construction, and youth league work, comprehensively reflecting the effectiveness of CASIL''s Party building efforts.', 0);

INSERT INTO pages (id, section, title_zh, title_en, content_zh, content_en, sort_order) VALUES ('party_dynamic', 'party', '黨建動態', 'Party Building News', '航天控股黨委堅持以習近平新時代中國特色社會主義思想為指導，深入學習貫徹黨的二十大精神，紮實開展主題教育活動，持續推進基層黨組織標準化規範化建設。

公司黨委定期組織理論學習中心組學習，舉辦專題黨課，開展紅色教育基地參觀學習等活動，不斷增強黨員幹部的政治意識、大局意識、核心意識、看齊意識。', 'The CASIL Party Committee adheres to the guidance of Xi Jinping Thought on Socialism with Chinese Characteristics for a New Era, deeply studies and implements the spirit of the 20th CPC National Congress, solidly carries out thematic education activities, and continuously promotes the standardized construction of grassroots Party organizations.

The Company''s Party Committee regularly organizes theoretical study sessions, holds thematic Party lectures, and conducts visits to revolutionary education bases, continuously enhancing the political consciousness, overall awareness, core awareness, and alignment awareness of Party members and cadres.', 1);

INSERT INTO pages (id, section, title_zh, title_en, content_zh, content_en, sort_order) VALUES ('party_pioneer', 'party', '黨員先鋒', 'Party Member Pioneers', '在航天控股改革發展的征程中，廣大黨員幹部衝鋒在前、勇挑重擔，在科研攻關、生產一線、管理創新等各個崗位上發揮先鋒模範作用。

本欄目集中展示公司優秀共產黨員的先進事蹟，他們以實際行動踐行初心使命，用汗水與智慧為航天事業貢獻力量，是新時代航天人的傑出代表。', 'In the journey of CASIL''s reform and development, Party members and cadres have charged ahead and shouldered heavy responsibilities, playing exemplary roles in scientific research, production, management innovation and various positions.

This section showcases the advanced deeds of the Company''s outstanding Communist Party members, who fulfill their original aspirations and mission through practical actions, contributing to the aerospace industry with their dedication and wisdom as outstanding representatives of aerospace professionals in the new era.', 2);

INSERT INTO pages (id, section, title_zh, title_en, content_zh, content_en, sort_order) VALUES ('party_staff', 'party', '職工之家', 'Staff Home', '航天控股始終堅持以人為本，關心關愛職工，積極構建和諧勞動關係。公司工會充分發揮橋樑紐帶作用，持續改善職工工作環境和生活條件，組織豐富多彩的文體活動，增強職工的歸屬感和幸福感。

公司設有完善的職工福利體系，包括健康體檢、困難職工幫扶、節日慰問等，讓每一位職工都能感受到航天大家庭的溫暖。', 'CASIL always adheres to a people-oriented approach, cares for its employees, and actively builds harmonious labor relations. The Company''s trade union fully plays its role as a bridge, continuously improves the working environment and living conditions of employees, organizes diverse cultural and sports activities, and enhances employees'' sense of belonging and well-being.

The Company has a comprehensive employee welfare system, including health check-ups, assistance for employees in need, and holiday greetings, ensuring that every employee feels the warmth of the CASIL family.', 3);

INSERT INTO pages (id, section, title_zh, title_en, content_zh, content_en, sort_order) VALUES ('party_youth', 'party', '團青風采', 'Youth Style', '航天控股團委緊跟黨委步伐，圍繞中心、服務大局，團結帶領廣大青年員工立足崗位、建功立業。公司團組織積極開展青年文明號創建、青年崗位能手評選、青年志願者服務等活動，為青年成長成才搭建平台。

青年員工是航天控股發展的生力軍，他們朝氣蓬勃、銳意進取，在各自崗位上綻放青春風采，為公司注入源源不斷的創新活力。', 'The CASIL Youth League Committee follows the pace of the Party Committee, focuses on the center and serves the overall situation, unites and leads young employees to achieve success based on their positions. The Company''s Youth League organizations actively carry out activities such as creating Youth Civilization Teams, selecting Youth Job Experts, and Youth Volunteer Services, building platforms for youth growth and development.

Young employees are the driving force of CASIL''s development. Energetic and enterprising, they display their youthful vitality in their respective positions, injecting continuous innovative energy into the Company.', 4);
